{"tid":1224821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"616 – speaker大作戰 一齊幫手打擊班犬","createTime":"2019-06-15T05:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T11:13:36.000Z","uid":83487,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c182133a1b7ec1b5ce2d2a5ad4e899242cd494c8","tid":1224821,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"見到有巴打話用播歐打片心理攻擊班犬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1224467/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1224467/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\n絕對認同呢個係一個非常好既方法<br />\n但係除咗大作戰之餘<br />\n聽日咁多位巴絲<br />\n都可以各自用類似既方法心理攻擊班犬<br />\n <br />\n相信大家都聽過16歲小妹妹呢段錄音<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Lam1Hey/videos/vb.450867315005279/877187595960923/?type=2&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLam1Hey%2Fvideos%2Fvb.450867315005279%2F877187595960923%2F%3Ftype%3D2%26theater&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlYleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=3d6c1441\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Lam1Hey/videos/vb.450867315005279/877187595960923/?type=2&amp;theater</a><br />\n <br />\n我相信只要有惻隱之心仲喺度既話<br />\n點都會俾佢呢段一路講一路喊到痴哂線既說話感動到<br />\n <br />\n所以大家可以既話<br />\n聽日如果見到d企喺度冇得行開既犬<br />\n不妨用幾分鐘時間 開返呢段錄音播俾佢聽<br />\n你播片 佢可以選擇唔睇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但你播錄音 佢冇得選擇唔聽</span></span><br />\n聽完之後 佢心裡面點諗 我地冇得控制<br />\n但同上面巴打大作戰既目的一樣<br />\n只要有一隻犬被打動 我哋就向成功踏前一小步<br />\n大家仲可以喺唔同地方一齊幫手打擊唔同既犬<br />\n <br />\n除咗上面小妹妹錄音之外<br />\n真正媽媽城姐企犬隻面前嗰段錄音<br />\n提及返點解佢哋當初要考警<br />\n呢段錄音都要播<br />\n <br />\n播放工具方<br />\n有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">bluetooth speaker</span></span>既<br />\n就聽日帶埋出嚟用佢播俾班犬聽<br />\n一定大聲過就咁用電話speaker<br />\n冇既 都可以試下照用speaker播<br />\n <br />\n希望大家可以一齊幫手<br />\n幫得幾多得幾多<br />\n616 我哋真係冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b455e42e529f29b63751c14297706d6a26f63b","tid":1224821,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b42bda39328539638c6be00dd1de9ec3ca975c1","tid":1224821,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a78921a796d0422a323716343dc0310f3a7dd1c","tid":1224821,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3465c8e0368fae9fc4329f382d219c9c4a995480","tid":1224821,"uid":85474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"6323cbc3370c4f9b4b558cfaf8fba50b1c480314","tid":1224821,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"香港警察 社會垃圾<br />\n人民奴隸 賣港惡賊<br />\n底層散仔毅進弱智仔<br />\n就算大學學歷都係垃圾科，無得揀先去做警犬嘅廢柴，蛇鼠一窩"},{"pid":"ac963fee245d055165f622ff7768e3de059eed49","tid":1224821,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"大家一齊幫手令更多犬唔撈"},{"pid":"ca6043f1d748db467f30f2d73c01fe3dd7a802f2","tid":1224821,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bea06332ec1bccfd45766c119a2ef378249816","tid":1224821,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"